Just, you know, "good race" and all that, 
the usual pleasantries.

114
00:05:15,133 --> 00:05:16,839
I'll pass that along, Keith.

115
00:05:17,032 --> 00:05:19,421
I'm sorry. Things are just 
a little busy here right now.

116
00:05:19,745 --> 00:05:21,679
Following up that lead 
on the bus crash, I hope.

117
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:24,866
They're checking out the front end, 
the brakes, everything.

118
00:05:25,057 --> 00:05:26,384
