223
00:10:39,190 --> 00:10:42,318
but dad's pretty conservative 
about fact-finding trips abroad.

224
00:10:47,443 --> 00:10:48,979
The calling cards Amelia took --

225
00:10:49,115 --> 00:10:51,239
did you jot the numbers down anywhere?

226
00:10:51,902 --> 00:10:56,037
So, the thong stays in the closet, 
and I hit the big Ibiza website.

227
00:10:56,436 --> 00:10:59,169
It's time to see if any 
of the party people of europe

228
